with patch.dict('os.environ', {'USER': 'dave', 'IS_SUPER': 'normal'}, clear
    =True):
    tf = self.tempfile()
    print('{"greeting": "Hello, $IS_SUPER $USER"}', file=tf)
    tf.close()
    try:
        c = Configure.open(tf.name)
        self.assertEqual(c['greeting'], 'Hello, normal dave')
    finally:
        os.unlink(tf.name)
